```plantuml
@startuml microsoft_covid19-BackToWork

actor Employee
participant "Healthcare Bot" as Bot
participant "Azure Function\n(Post/Get Handlers)" as Function
participant "DbHelper" as DB
participant "Azure SQL Database" as SQL
participant "NotificationHelper" as Notify
participant "SendGrid" as Email

Employee -> Bot: Start health assessment
Bot -> Employee: Request personal info
Employee -> Bot: Provide personal info
Bot -> Function: POST /userinfo
Function -> DB: SaveUserInfo()
DB -> SQL: Execute stored procedure
SQL --> DB: Success
DB --> Function: Success
Function --> Bot: Success

Bot -> Employee: Request symptoms
Employee -> Bot: Provide symptoms
Bot -> Function: POST /symptoms
Function -> DB: SaveSymptomsInfo()
DB -> SQL: Execute stored procedure
SQL --> DB: Success
DB --> Function: Success
Function --> Bot: Success

Bot -> Employee: Request lab results
Employee -> Bot: Provide lab results
Bot -> Function: POST /labtest
Function -> DB: SaveLabTestInfo()
DB -> SQL: Execute stored procedure
SQL --> DB: Success
DB --> Function: Success
Function --> Bot: Success

Bot -> Function: GET /requeststatus
Function -> DB: GetRequestStatus()
DB -> SQL: Execute stored procedure
SQL --> DB: Status data
DB --> Function: Status data
Function --> Bot: Status data

Bot -> Function: POST /notify
Function -> Notify: SendNotification()
Notify -> Email: Send email with QR code
Email --> Notify: Success
Notify --> Function: Success
Function --> Bot: Success

Bot -> Employee: Show clearance status\n+ QR code if cleared

@enduml
```